nodes.text: Chenini was one of the three moons of the planet Tatooine, along with Guermessa and Ghomrassen. Chenini and its parent planet were located in the Tatoo system, a binary star system located in the Arkanis sector of the Outer Rim Territories.
The moon is also the name of a real village near Tataouine in Tunisia, where many Tatooine scenes were filmed.
